{
  "stem": "25809.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then in the afternoon, from cigar boxes-- little cigar boxes-- a knife and, and a brick, we constructed a castle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The castle was about this big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we kind of created our own toy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the, the castle had a bridge that could be raised.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had-- we took the hinges from the, from the, the cigar boxes, because they had hinges on them, and with that we could hinge the, the drawbridge.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And for years that castle was kept by the van Amerongens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I, I, I-- they may still have it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we created [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like a medieval castle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we played with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had fun with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we put it-- we put those castles together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Maybe we made more than one castle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And during the warm days, they had a little balcony.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the balcony was like, oh, yay high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I would get a, a big tub of water and splash myself with, with water to stay cool and, and lay on the balcony.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I could not raise myself above the railing of the balcony because then people could see me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I made sure I stayed below the, the level that the balcony was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We-- Andre and I-- I was a little kid, so I didn't need that much space to sleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And Andre was a teenager at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So between the two of us, we slept in a, in a bed that was actually a one-person big bed, but we slept there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The two of us, we slept there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never left the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was just-- and, and I wouldn't even go near the window because the people across the street could see us.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
